SP.POP.TOTL.label: Total Population (in number of people)
SP.POP.TOTL.info: Total population is based on the de facto definition of population, which counts all residents regardless of legal status or citizenship--except for refugees not permanently settled in the country of asylum, who are generally considered part of the population of their country of origin. The values shown are midyear estimates.
